-- India's L&T to hold on to Satyam stake: CFO
-- 
-- Mon Apr 13, 2009 3:19am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/04/13/us-satyam-ltstake-sb-idUSTRE53C0WY20090413

 

 MUMBAI  (Reuters) - India's Larsen & Toubro ( LART.BO ), which has built up a 12 percent stake in Satyam Computer Services SATY.BO, plans to hold on to the stake, its chief financial officer said on television channel NDTV Profit. 

 Earlier Satyam SAY.N named mid-sized outsourcer Tech Mahindra ( TEML.BO ) as the highest bidder for it. (Reporting by  Narayanan Somasundaram ; Editing by Rosemary Arackaparambil)